  "title": "CheckboxRequiredValidator",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator\", \"name\": \"CheckboxRequiredValidator\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L195-L233\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/11.0.0-next.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L195-L233\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"checkboxrequiredvalidator\">CheckboxRequiredValidator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#checkboxrequiredvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>A Directive that adds the <code>required</code> validator to checkbox controls marked with the\n<code>required</code> attribute. The directive is provided with the <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> multi-provider list.</p>\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">See also<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">Form Validation</a></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  <h2 id=\"ngmodules\">NgModules<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#ngmodules\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul class=\"ngmodule-list\">\n\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">FormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  \n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">ReactiveFormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n  \n</ul>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">Selectors<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <ul>\n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][required][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    \n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][required][formControl]</code></li>\n    \n    <li><code>input[type=checkbox][required][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n    \n  </ul>\n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"inherited-members-list\">\n  <h3 id=\"inherited-from-requiredvalidator\">Inherited from <code><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator\">RequiredValidator</a></code><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#inherited-from-requiredvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li>\n        <code><a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#required\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@Input()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">required</span>: boolean | string</a></code>\n    </li>\n  \n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n  <section class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\">Adding a required checkbox validator using template-driven forms<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<p>The following example shows how to add a checkbox required validator to an input attached to an\nngModel binding.</p>\n<code-example>\n&#x3C;input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"active\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> required>\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/Validator\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#adding-a-required-checkbox-validator-using-template-driven-forms\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#checkboxrequiredvalidator\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#description\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#inherited-from-requiredvalidator\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#ngmodules\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#see-also\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator#selectors\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#required\n - guide/form-validation\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L195-L233\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/11.0.0-next.0/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L195-L233\n-->"
